WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.230 --> 02:49.970
[Episode 9]

03:11.620 --> 03:13.490
Why is there an evil aura in Yi City?

03:13.970 --> 03:15.600
What is the evil aura?

03:15.930 --> 03:17.290
Heaven and earth produce spiritual energy.

03:17.450 --> 03:19.370
Eternals and demons all cultivate with this spiritual energy.

03:20.130 --> 03:21.079
Yet evil aura

03:21.110 --> 03:22.850
specifically comes from evil cultivators.

03:22.870 --> 03:23.980
Evil cultivators?

03:24.060 --> 03:25.850
They cultivate by devouring essence.

03:27.040 --> 03:28.250
Since there's an evil aura,

03:29.079 --> 03:30.300
there must be

03:30.410 --> 03:31.660
evil cultivators in Yi City.

03:31.680 --> 03:33.090
Devouring essence...

03:34.420 --> 03:36.540
The Desireless Stone led us to this Yi City.

03:36.650 --> 03:38.090
So is the appearance of the evil cultivator

03:38.120 --> 03:39.820
related to the next Contemplation?

03:59.480 --> 04:00.210
Bai Shuo?

04:01.000 --> 04:01.810
Bai Shuo!

04:20.180 --> 04:22.820
Fan Yue? Fan Yue!

04:53.840 --> 04:55.200
Mana is banned in Yi City.

04:55.220 --> 04:56.580
But it's not working on her?

05:01.310 --> 05:02.360
Fan Yue!

05:03.070 --> 05:04.980
I once saw this monster in the Desireless Stone.

05:06.090 --> 05:06.850
Let's go.

05:08.000 --> 05:08.730
Shuo.

05:10.790 --> 05:12.180
Stay out of the Bright Moon Palace's business.

05:22.580 --> 05:23.410
Who are you?

05:23.440 --> 05:24.640
How dare you break into Yi Palace?

05:24.750 --> 05:25.880
Yi Palace?

05:27.710 --> 05:28.780
Don't be rude.

05:31.680 --> 05:32.390
Back off.

05:32.420 --> 05:33.210
Yes, sir.

05:34.730 --> 05:36.060
I didn't expect you, the Master of Bright Moon Palace,

05:36.090 --> 05:37.710
would join the competition in person.

05:37.740 --> 05:39.510
Earlier today, with the Eternals and demons around,

05:39.530 --> 05:41.230
I couldn't expose our collaboration with you.

05:41.330 --> 05:42.980
Please forgive me

05:43.120 --> 05:44.450
for my disrespect.

05:45.040 --> 05:46.190
Let's cut to the chase.

05:46.930 --> 05:48.200
Just now,

05:48.340 --> 05:50.260
I saw some evil aura entering Yi Palace.

05:51.950 --> 05:53.310
Did you see it wrong, Master Fan?

05:53.950 --> 05:55.590
There has never been any evil cultivator in Yi City.

05:55.610 --> 05:57.030
How could there be an evil aura?

05:57.060 --> 05:58.310
It can't be wrong.

05:58.340 --> 05:59.670
We've been chasing him all the way here.

05:59.700 --> 06:01.400
We saw him entering Yi Palace.

06:01.420 --> 06:02.860
Go with me to find him if you don't believe us.

06:03.590 --> 06:05.300
Since you saw it with your own eyes, Master Fan,

06:05.320 --> 06:07.260
I will report this to His Majesty right away

06:07.280 --> 06:08.340
and search the palace.

06:08.370 --> 06:10.080
However, this is Yi Palace after all.

06:10.100 --> 06:10.930
It's in the dead of night.

06:10.950 --> 06:12.630
I'm afraid it's improper for you to enter the palace now.

06:14.360 --> 06:16.270
I've told you about the evil aura and the evil cultivator.

06:16.410 --> 06:17.420
Whether you investigate it or not

06:17.610 --> 06:18.720
is up to you.

06:18.800 --> 06:20.700
Evil cultivators are banished by the Three Races

06:20.940 --> 06:22.690
If there's really an evil cultivator in the city,

06:22.790 --> 06:24.230
our Yi Clan will not let him go for sure.

06:26.390 --> 06:26.930
Let's go.

06:36.320 --> 06:37.270
You could clearly tell that

06:37.300 --> 06:38.630
the lieutenant of the King of Yi tried to stop us on purpose

06:38.650 --> 06:40.000
from entering the palace to investigate the monster.

06:40.030 --> 06:41.340
Why did you give in so easily?

06:41.370 --> 06:43.690
If that monster is really related to the King of Yi,

06:43.720 --> 06:44.960
what do you think

06:44.980 --> 06:46.430
you can find out in that way?

06:46.460 --> 06:48.020
You'd even die in there.

06:49.530 --> 06:50.800
You don't need to make up these excuses.

06:51.610 --> 06:52.990
As the prestigious Master of Bright Moon Palace,

06:53.040 --> 06:54.960
how could you let them shut you out of the palace gate

06:54.990 --> 06:56.120
just for your worry

06:56.120 --> 06:57.390
about my life?

06:57.390 --> 06:58.120
Master.

07:00.330 --> 07:00.920
Master,

07:00.970 --> 07:02.170
did you hunt that monster down?

07:02.570 --> 07:03.490
That monster

07:04.440 --> 07:05.230
entered Yi Palace.

07:06.150 --> 07:07.420
You came just in time.

07:07.830 --> 07:08.800
Tell me,

07:09.270 --> 07:10.360
who on earth are you?

07:11.460 --> 07:13.270
I found you kinda weird

07:13.290 --> 07:15.120
before we entered Yi City.

07:15.180 --> 07:17.370
You seem to be very sensitive to things in here.

07:17.390 --> 07:18.780
Spiritual power is banned in Yi City.

07:18.820 --> 07:20.990
Even Fan Yue is restricted by the rules.

07:21.020 --> 07:22.960
But you can use your spiritual power.

07:22.990 --> 07:24.840
Are you a Yi citizen?

07:25.370 --> 07:27.520
Yi citizens are born with limited spiritual power.

07:27.540 --> 07:30.830
But your power is so strong that you can kill a thousand with a single strike.

07:30.860 --> 07:33.330
It's enough to make you the guardian of Bright Moon Palace.

07:33.350 --> 07:34.840
Are you a human or a demon?

07:34.870 --> 07:36.040
It's none of your business.

07:36.320 --> 07:37.350
None of my business?

07:37.680 --> 07:39.590
I made a deal with your Bright Moon Palace.

07:39.630 --> 07:41.659
Since it's a deal, we should trust each other.

07:41.690 --> 07:43.490
There's a lot going on in Yi City right now.

07:43.510 --> 07:44.880
Your identity is fishy.

07:44.909 --> 07:46.430
I can stop the deal.

07:47.159 --> 07:49.270
It's not up to you.

07:51.070 --> 07:52.510
You should have known

07:52.560 --> 07:54.060
the real identity of Tian Huo, right?

07:54.090 --> 07:55.440
Tian Huo's identity

07:55.460 --> 07:56.700
has nothing to do with claiming the Heart Flames

07:56.730 --> 07:57.659
and gathering the Five Contemplations.

07:58.230 --> 07:59.230
Fan Yue,

07:59.260 --> 08:00.700
I know you are quite mighty,

08:00.720 --> 08:01.930
and I can't beat you.

08:01.960 --> 08:03.040
But it doesn't mean

08:03.060 --> 08:05.550
I have to accept your schemes and deception.

08:05.580 --> 08:07.470
I can ignore her identity,

08:07.590 --> 08:10.100
but I need trust and respect for our cooperation.

08:18.780 --> 08:19.660
Tian Huo,

08:20.430 --> 08:21.660
you may leave now.

08:21.860 --> 08:23.290
Yes, Master.

08:27.750 --> 08:28.870
Tian Huo

08:29.200 --> 08:30.480
is indeed a Yi citizen.

08:30.790 --> 08:33.110
As for why she has the extraordinary spiritual power out of limits,

08:33.140 --> 08:34.669
this is her own business.

08:34.730 --> 08:35.830
It has nothing to do with us.

08:36.640 --> 08:37.429
Fine.

08:37.929 --> 08:39.289
Everyone has secrets.

08:39.320 --> 08:40.480
I can stop asking about it.

08:41.169 --> 08:42.679
But since she is a Yi citizen,

08:42.700 --> 08:44.670
she must know this city well.

08:44.700 --> 08:46.220
When looking for the entrance to Yi City,

08:46.240 --> 08:47.840
I almost died in the sand formation.

08:48.520 --> 08:50.240
Did Tian Huo provide any clues?

08:51.200 --> 08:52.900
Tian Huo's been by my side for seven years.

08:53.170 --> 08:55.450
She's never had any contact with Yi City over the past seven years.

08:55.880 --> 08:58.040
The entrance to Yi City changes every year.

08:58.150 --> 08:59.180
None of us—

08:59.310 --> 09:00.540
neither you, me,

09:00.590 --> 09:01.260
nor Tian Huo—

09:01.290 --> 09:02.500
know the specific location.

09:02.520 --> 09:04.440
But now that we're in Yi City,

09:04.500 --> 09:06.190
is she still clueless

09:06.220 --> 09:07.140
about the three Heart Flames?

09:07.160 --> 09:08.180
Yes.

09:08.290 --> 09:09.180
So,

09:09.200 --> 09:10.680
you've never doubted her?

09:10.720 --> 09:11.630
Never.

09:11.650 --> 09:12.740
You can totally trust her,

09:12.770 --> 09:13.930
but why should I?

09:13.950 --> 09:15.310
Because you have to trust me completely.

09:17.860 --> 09:19.310
I can't trust anyone

09:19.340 --> 09:20.780
except myself.

09:22.720 --> 09:24.640
Here's my promise to protect you.

09:24.670 --> 09:25.910
I can assure you that,

09:25.930 --> 09:27.570
as long as I'm alive,

09:27.680 --> 09:28.960
I will let no one hurt you.

09:37.620 --> 09:39.380
Sounds quite touching.

09:40.640 --> 09:41.690
Fan Yue,

09:42.140 --> 09:44.020
you're giving it your all

09:44.670 --> 09:45.610
to protect the Desireless Stone,

09:46.430 --> 09:47.630
not me.

09:51.060 --> 09:54.030
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

09:54.450 --> 09:57.720
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

09:58.110 --> 10:01.490
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

09:59.350 --> 10:00.280
What?

10:00.330 --> 10:01.360
Isn't that the truth?

10:01.770 --> 10:04.500
♫This moment feels like forever♫

10:04.420 --> 10:05.790
Of course, you can think that way.

10:04.850 --> 10:07.500
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

10:06.840 --> 10:07.960
So,

10:07.960 --> 10:11.700
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

10:08.150 --> 10:09.170
don't make any reckless moves,

10:09.190 --> 10:10.380
and don't be delusional.

10:10.720 --> 10:12.970
Zero in on looking for the Heart Flame and Five Contemplations.

10:11.990 --> 10:13.920
♫Even if I'll perish♫

10:13.210 --> 10:15.390
That's all

10:14.210 --> 10:16.790
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

10:15.760 --> 10:16.660
I need you to do.

10:16.910 --> 10:20.040
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

10:18.680 --> 10:20.100
OK! That's all!

10:20.230 --> 10:21.480
Once we're done with it,

10:20.390 --> 10:28.770
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

10:21.510 --> 10:22.520
there's gonna be

10:22.550 --> 10:23.520
no more ties between us!

10:52.300 --> 10:54.090
It's been seven years since I was last in Yi City.

10:54.890 --> 10:56.430
Feels like it's changed a lot.

10:57.190 --> 10:58.310
Even a person

10:58.930 --> 11:00.150
can change a lot

11:00.860 --> 11:02.940
in seven years, not to mention a city.

11:02.970 --> 11:04.250
I know Hua Lin well.

11:04.920 --> 11:06.980
Everything happening in Yi City

11:07.000 --> 11:08.670
is under his surveillance.

11:08.700 --> 11:10.860
There's no way he doesn't know about the monster.

11:11.900 --> 11:13.900
The Three Races forbid evil cultivation.

11:14.510 --> 11:16.540
If that evil being is really related to the King of Yi,

11:17.660 --> 11:18.990
then both the Eternal and Demon Races

11:19.170 --> 11:20.890
will surely go after the entire Yi Clan.

11:22.910 --> 11:24.200
Don't worry, Master.

11:24.440 --> 11:26.270
I've cut ties with the Yi Clan

11:26.450 --> 11:28.320
ever since my departure seven years ago.

11:28.640 --> 11:31.520
Now I'm back here just to get the Contemplation for you.

11:31.790 --> 11:33.590
I will get to the bottom of the monster as soon as possible.

11:45.000 --> 11:46.480
General, what's wrong?

11:46.960 --> 11:47.840
You go first.

11:47.910 --> 11:49.070
I'll be right there.

11:49.120 --> 11:49.870
Yes, General.

12:07.520 --> 12:09.280
General, you're really vigilant.

12:11.090 --> 12:12.760
I watched you grow up.

12:12.970 --> 12:14.490
How could I not know it was you?

12:16.600 --> 12:17.470
Princess.

12:17.590 --> 12:19.310
I've already cut ties with Yi City.

12:19.340 --> 12:20.760
I'm not your Princess.

12:23.220 --> 12:23.650
Hua Hong...

12:23.680 --> 12:25.070
Don't call me that.

12:25.090 --> 12:27.090
I am the guardian of Bright Moon Palace, Tian Huo.

12:31.180 --> 12:32.500
Lady Tian Huo,

12:32.520 --> 12:34.180
how have you been these years?

12:34.340 --> 12:36.210
I'm not here to catch up with you.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.040
Why is there a monster in the palace?

12:39.890 --> 12:41.370
I don't know what you're talking about.

12:41.490 --> 12:42.700
Stop playing dumb here.

12:43.930 --> 12:45.370
I'm patrolling with the guards.

12:45.400 --> 12:47.240
Nothing suspicious was found.

12:47.260 --> 12:48.210
Don't worry.

12:48.260 --> 12:49.990
If there is really an evil being in the palace,

12:50.020 --> 12:51.570
His Majesty and I will show no mercy.

12:53.480 --> 12:55.270
You're still as hypocritical

12:55.550 --> 12:56.910
as before.

12:57.470 --> 12:58.870
You clearly know

12:58.890 --> 13:00.250
whether there's a demon in the palace.

13:00.270 --> 13:01.940
If Eternals and demons find out about it,

13:01.970 --> 13:04.450
I'm afraid the Yi City you've been swearing to protect

13:04.510 --> 13:06.280
will fall apart.

13:07.260 --> 13:08.420
The palace is a sacred place.

13:08.450 --> 13:09.380
No evil beings are allowed here.

13:09.840 --> 13:11.800
So you don't need to worry about that, Lady Tian Huo.

13:12.450 --> 13:14.230
The fate of Yi City doesn't concern me.

13:15.740 --> 13:17.260
Where is the second Heart Flame?

13:18.320 --> 13:20.930
Since you're joining the Wutong Martial Arts Contest as Lady Tian Huo,

13:22.240 --> 13:24.520
you should abide by the rules and keep it fair.

13:24.540 --> 13:26.340
Who are you to talk about fairness with me?

13:29.120 --> 13:30.230
No matter what,

13:30.670 --> 13:32.380
I'm your uncle.

13:32.410 --> 13:33.370
Uncle?

13:34.390 --> 13:35.240
Yes.

13:36.150 --> 13:37.970
You are my mother's sworn brother.

13:38.100 --> 13:39.920
My grandfather raised you up.

13:40.640 --> 13:42.240
The Mei Family helped you and the King of Yi get to where you are today

13:42.270 --> 13:43.000
with all the glory.

13:43.000 --> 13:44.390
But how did you treat her?

13:44.730 --> 13:46.560
Now you wanna talk about fairness with me?

13:47.150 --> 13:49.390
Where were you when my mother was forced to death?

13:50.280 --> 13:51.910
The Mei Family has been loyal to Yi King for generations.

13:52.760 --> 13:55.120
Your mother died for the whole Yi City.

13:55.140 --> 13:56.540
If you insist on blaming her death

13:56.570 --> 13:57.610
on me,

13:57.970 --> 13:59.050
then do it.

13:59.700 --> 14:00.680
I'll repay the Mei Family

14:01.310 --> 14:02.470
with my life.

14:22.510 --> 14:27.470
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

14:23.610 --> 14:24.750
Stop!

14:30.630 --> 14:36.240
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

14:31.820 --> 14:32.650
Your Majesty.

14:38.950 --> 14:46.350
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

14:47.270 --> 14:52.460
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

14:49.570 --> 14:50.920
You left years ago.

14:50.950 --> 14:52.220
Why are you back now?

14:52.300 --> 14:53.580
To get the Heart Flame,

14:53.740 --> 14:54.990
you gotta rely on your real capacities.

14:56.180 --> 14:57.420
What's your position

14:57.450 --> 14:58.930
to be snooping around here?

14:59.120 --> 15:00.720
Any position will do,

15:01.060 --> 15:02.900
but it can never be a Yi citizen.

15:04.630 --> 15:06.200
Since you're an outsider...

15:07.280 --> 15:08.000
Wu Zhao,

15:08.920 --> 15:10.400
arrest this intruder who dared

15:10.420 --> 15:11.260
to trespass the palace.

15:10.990 --> 15:14.710
♫Across thousands of miles♫

15:11.280 --> 15:12.310
Your Majesty,

15:12.390 --> 15:14.320
Lady Tian Huo is the guardian of Bright Moon Palace.

15:14.340 --> 15:16.500
It's not the right time to mess with the Master of Bright Moon Palace.

15:16.530 --> 15:17.770
Please think twice, Your Majesty.

15:18.280 --> 15:19.040
Get lost!

15:19.490 --> 15:21.250
Get out of the palace right now!

15:19.530 --> 15:24.380
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

15:21.280 --> 15:22.770
Get out of Yi City!

15:22.910 --> 15:24.200
And never come back!

15:24.960 --> 15:26.490
Once I get the Heart Flame,

15:26.950 --> 15:34.440
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

15:27.260 --> 15:29.300
I'll never see you again.

15:35.250 --> 15:40.360
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

15:45.840 --> 15:47.370
Your Majesty, you've been missing the Princess every day.

15:47.910 --> 15:49.790
Now you finally met her today.

15:49.790 --> 15:51.550
Why did you say those angry words?

15:52.600 --> 15:54.440
She shouldn't be back now.

15:54.910 --> 15:56.120
They have noticed him.

15:56.840 --> 15:58.470
They won't let it go for sure.

15:58.500 --> 15:59.770
At this point,

16:00.490 --> 16:02.140
we have no choice but to play along with the plan

16:02.160 --> 16:03.390
and advance it.

16:03.410 --> 16:04.440
What about the Princess?

16:04.460 --> 16:06.180
if she gets in the way,

16:06.940 --> 16:08.260
show no mercy.

16:10.600 --> 16:11.330
Yes, Your Majesty.

16:35.890 --> 16:36.980
Senior Chong Zhao!

16:37.000 --> 16:38.300
Where have you been so late at night?

16:38.320 --> 16:39.370
Is Bai Shuo back?

16:39.400 --> 16:40.920
I saw her going back to her room.

16:40.940 --> 16:42.100
What happened?

16:52.450 --> 16:53.870
Of course, you can think that way.

16:53.890 --> 16:54.580
So,

16:54.610 --> 16:56.300
don't make any reckless moves, and don't be delusional.

16:56.890 --> 16:59.410
Zero in on looking for the Heart Flame and Five Contemplations.

16:59.600 --> 17:00.780
That's all

17:01.090 --> 17:02.210
I need you

17:02.240 --> 17:02.980
to do.

17:05.400 --> 17:06.440
That's right.

17:07.250 --> 17:08.390
That's all.

17:09.190 --> 17:10.280
Shuo.

17:11.740 --> 17:12.540
Shuo.

17:17.770 --> 17:19.300
I'm glad you're alright.

17:19.380 --> 17:20.240
That monster...

17:20.240 --> 17:21.579
Something is wrong with Yi City.

17:21.599 --> 17:23.200
If there is no reason to stay,

17:23.220 --> 17:24.339
you should leave immediately.

17:24.490 --> 17:25.310
I know.

17:26.329 --> 17:27.050
I saw

17:27.730 --> 17:28.569
Fu Ling earlier today.

17:34.370 --> 17:36.570
Sounds quite touching.

17:36.600 --> 17:37.500
Fan Yue,

17:37.680 --> 17:39.420
you're giving it your all

17:39.490 --> 17:40.380
to protect the Desireless Stone,

17:40.650 --> 17:41.890
not me.

17:52.180 --> 17:52.900
Come in.

18:04.360 --> 18:05.530
Did you see Hua Lin?

18:07.540 --> 18:08.490
What did he say?

18:08.730 --> 18:10.610
He denied his connection with the monster

18:10.830 --> 18:12.440
and just asked me to get out of Yi City.

18:15.490 --> 18:16.640
Looks like we need to grab

18:16.640 --> 18:17.720
the Heart Flame real quick this time.

18:18.960 --> 18:20.880
Although I don't know the King of Yi well,

18:20.900 --> 18:22.980
he used to be a great figure with his reputation spreading everywhere.

18:23.690 --> 18:25.020
As a father,

18:25.200 --> 18:26.920
he hasn't seen you for seven years.

18:26.990 --> 18:28.670
Yet he asked you to get out of Yi City as soon as he met you.

18:28.690 --> 18:30.550
They might sound like angry words,

18:30.670 --> 18:32.290
but he might be speaking the truth.

18:32.430 --> 18:33.760
I'm afraid you've overthought it, Master.

18:34.400 --> 18:36.250
He doesn't live up to his reputation.

18:36.270 --> 18:37.590
He doesn't deserve to be a king,

18:37.760 --> 18:39.260
much less my father.

18:39.450 --> 18:40.360
No matter what,

18:41.290 --> 18:42.560
the current priority

18:43.130 --> 18:44.690
is to find the Heart Flame.

18:47.480 --> 18:49.680
Why didn't you tell me that Fu Ling was there?

18:49.990 --> 18:51.510
You'd definitely try to kill her if you saw her.

18:51.540 --> 18:52.160
But that

18:52.160 --> 18:53.160
wouldn't do you any good.

18:53.160 --> 18:54.090
So,

18:54.240 --> 18:56.160
you made a decision for me once again.

18:57.560 --> 18:58.720
I just wanted to keep you safe.

18:58.750 --> 19:00.160
That's your personal thought!

19:04.150 --> 19:05.050
Chong Zhao,

19:06.040 --> 19:08.270
I don't wanna quarrel with you because of this case.

19:08.410 --> 19:10.590
I know I can't kill her now.

19:10.800 --> 19:12.380
I will try to survive

19:12.510 --> 19:14.790
and give a fatal blow to her and Zhen Yu in the future.

19:14.810 --> 19:16.330
But Fu Ling came to Yi City.

19:16.360 --> 19:17.950
This thing can't be as simple as it seems to be.

19:18.280 --> 19:19.720
If you get any other information,

19:20.230 --> 19:21.560
I hope you won't hide it from me.

19:22.680 --> 19:23.460
Okay.

19:24.350 --> 19:25.390
I promise you.

19:31.060 --> 19:32.230
Good night.

19:45.400 --> 19:46.480
If you need anything,

19:46.500 --> 19:47.780
feel free to call me anytime.

19:57.390 --> 19:58.460
Seems like

19:58.480 --> 20:00.800
she can't completely break off with Chong Zhao.

20:01.070 --> 20:02.270
Chong Zhao

20:02.850 --> 20:04.590
can't get in the way of my plan.

20:04.820 --> 20:06.560
What if he's in the way of something else?

20:08.550 --> 20:09.580
What are you trying to say?

20:10.470 --> 20:11.370
Nothing.

20:11.410 --> 20:12.610
Please take a good rest, Master

20:18.550 --> 20:22.850
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

20:26.120 --> 20:29.600
♫You are my distant call♫

20:30.210 --> 20:34.870
♫You are my first and last♫

20:35.310 --> 20:41.340
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

20:41.660 --> 20:44.760
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

20:45.200 --> 20:49.080
♫Let's never let go♫

20:45.870 --> 20:48.490
[Sihai Inn]

20:59.810 --> 21:01.920
Lady Tian Huo, you've made a name with your prowess.

21:01.950 --> 21:03.430
Yet your dining etiquette is so good.

21:04.000 --> 21:06.330
Is it your Yi citizens' habit?

21:06.700 --> 21:08.070
Don't talk when eating. Don't ask too much.

21:10.900 --> 21:11.820
Sirs and madams,

21:11.850 --> 21:12.550
a gentleman

21:12.550 --> 21:14.030
just asked me to send you this box of cakes.

21:15.390 --> 21:16.220
Please enjoy.

21:17.280 --> 21:18.160
Where is he?

21:18.440 --> 21:19.080
He just left.

21:23.900 --> 21:25.460
Don't be too nosy.

21:33.350 --> 21:34.150
Hua Yong.

21:35.220 --> 21:36.800
[Hua Yong, Yi Clan, Prince of Yi]

21:36.030 --> 21:36.840
Sister.

21:37.110 --> 21:38.550
Don't call me that!

21:39.970 --> 21:41.210
It's disgusting.

21:42.620 --> 21:43.600
I told you

21:43.630 --> 21:45.840
never to show up in front of me ever again.

21:46.620 --> 21:48.070
I thought you came back

21:48.090 --> 21:49.280
because you had forgiven me.

21:49.680 --> 21:50.850
Forgive you?

21:51.480 --> 21:52.240
Just a box of cakes,

21:52.240 --> 21:53.720
and you want me to forget about everything from the past?

21:54.080 --> 21:55.080
No, it's not like that...

21:55.100 --> 21:56.050
Shut up!

21:56.780 --> 21:58.540
I'm warning you one last time.

21:58.850 --> 22:00.200
I've cut ties

22:00.890 --> 22:02.400
with you.

22:02.800 --> 22:04.260
If you show up again,

22:04.810 --> 22:06.240
I will beat you up.

22:15.010 --> 22:16.160
Stay out

22:16.240 --> 22:17.040
of Tian Huo's business.

22:27.180 --> 22:29.150
Who says I wanna get involved in her business?

22:29.260 --> 22:30.450
Now that we've obtained the first Heart Flame,

22:30.480 --> 22:31.850
I'm in a hurry to find the second one.

22:32.550 --> 22:33.250
By yourself?

22:34.020 --> 22:34.840
Can't I?

22:34.940 --> 22:35.830
Where are you going to find it?

22:36.910 --> 22:39.220
Since you haven't been honest with me, Master Fan,

22:39.320 --> 22:41.210
why should I tell you everything?

22:48.130 --> 22:49.010
Master,

22:49.190 --> 22:50.650
what's wrong with her today?

22:50.850 --> 22:52.130
Are you really letting her go alone?

22:52.890 --> 22:54.220
She can walk by herself

22:54.290 --> 22:55.680
and go anywhere she wants.

22:55.710 --> 22:57.190
What if she runs into danger?

22:57.810 --> 22:58.640
Danger?

22:59.250 --> 23:00.530
It's her own decision.

23:01.510 --> 23:03.140
There's no one else to blame if she dies.

23:03.900 --> 23:04.770
Mommy,

23:04.800 --> 23:06.240
what is this character?

23:06.840 --> 23:08.030
"Citizen."

23:08.050 --> 23:09.340
The "citizen" in "Yi citizen."

23:09.370 --> 23:12.460
What's the difference between humans and Yi citizens?

23:12.690 --> 23:13.890
There's not much difference.

23:15.460 --> 23:18.440
They're all made of flesh and bones,

23:18.630 --> 23:19.940
standing tall and upright.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.130
It's you.

23:21.150 --> 23:22.020
Why are you here?

23:23.000 --> 23:24.400
I'm here to deliver the medicine for Hu.

23:25.690 --> 23:26.650
Also,

23:26.680 --> 23:27.530
I'm here to ask you something.

23:29.150 --> 23:30.780
Hu, go play nearby.

23:30.880 --> 23:32.440
I'll teach you to read later,

23:32.470 --> 23:33.000
okay?

23:33.000 --> 23:33.640
Okay.

23:34.110 --> 23:34.680
Good girl.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.720
What do you want to ask?

23:39.070 --> 23:41.050
Do you know where the second Heart Flame is?

23:41.070 --> 23:42.900
Heart Flames choose their owners themselves.

23:42.920 --> 23:44.160
How would I know?

23:44.570 --> 23:45.890
Then do you know there's a monster

23:45.910 --> 23:47.080
in the city?

23:47.170 --> 23:48.320
Did it attack you?

23:49.070 --> 23:50.630
So, you knew it.

23:50.650 --> 23:51.890
What is it?

23:52.300 --> 23:53.800
No one knows what it is.

23:54.050 --> 23:56.050
We only know that it first appeared

23:56.100 --> 23:57.970
on a night seven years ago.

23:58.000 --> 23:59.350
Seven years ago again?

23:59.470 --> 24:02.200
That year, it bit many people in the city to death

24:02.330 --> 24:04.370
and then disappeared for a long time.

24:04.650 --> 24:07.030
After that, we heard about it from time to time.

24:07.050 --> 24:09.870
Some said it was formed from the souls of deceased Yi citizens.

24:10.030 --> 24:12.730
Some said it was a beast cultivated by an evil cultivator.

24:12.880 --> 24:14.670
But there was no conclusion.

24:15.620 --> 24:17.950
Later, His Majesty worried that there would be chaos among the people,

24:17.970 --> 24:20.210
so he ordered us to stop discussing this matter.

24:20.310 --> 24:22.190
Does it only come out at night?

24:22.210 --> 24:23.340
Maybe.

24:23.370 --> 24:25.130
No one has ever seen it during the day anyway.

24:25.810 --> 24:27.730
Do you know anything else?

24:29.470 --> 24:30.470
Don't ask too much

24:30.490 --> 24:32.210
about Yi citizens.

24:32.990 --> 24:34.430
I told you this

24:34.450 --> 24:36.330
to repay your kindness to Hu.

24:36.570 --> 24:37.920
Just now, you said

24:37.950 --> 24:39.760
Yi citizens were no different from humans.

24:39.890 --> 24:40.870
You were wrong.

24:41.070 --> 24:42.790
Yi citizens' suffering

24:42.810 --> 24:43.960
is not something Eternals, demons,

24:43.990 --> 24:45.210
and you humans

24:45.230 --> 24:46.600
can understand.

24:47.640 --> 24:48.570
Go.

24:48.740 --> 24:50.150
That's all I can say.

24:50.980 --> 24:53.030
Your friend's been waiting for you over there for a long time.

24:53.050 --> 24:54.230
Go back early.

24:55.060 --> 24:57.440
It's not safe in the city at night.

25:08.520 --> 25:10.090
Why did you follow me here?

25:10.120 --> 25:11.260
Don't play dumb.

25:11.290 --> 25:12.860
Don't act innocent after getting the benefit.

25:12.890 --> 25:15.530
I knew you wouldn't let me die,

25:15.740 --> 25:17.980
so I dared to come and go recklessly.

25:18.200 --> 25:19.510
I advise you not to play your tricks

25:19.510 --> 25:20.510
on me.

25:22.510 --> 25:24.030
But you still came.

25:25.570 --> 25:26.800
It won't happen again.

25:27.600 --> 25:28.710
Got it.

25:29.420 --> 25:31.330
It's getting late. Let's go back.

25:31.840 --> 25:33.390
I don't want to meet the monster again.

25:34.540 --> 25:35.950
Stop ordering me around.

25:37.300 --> 25:39.360
Got it. Don't be so verbose.

25:39.750 --> 25:41.140
I'm verbose?

25:41.170 --> 25:42.340
You keep emphasizing your identity.

25:42.360 --> 25:43.470
Aren't you verbose?

25:43.500 --> 25:44.670
Say that again!

25:44.690 --> 25:46.080
I dare not.

25:59.350 --> 26:00.190
Your Majesty,

26:00.370 --> 26:01.680
the first Heart Flame

26:01.700 --> 26:03.420
has been sent to Bai Shuo as planned.

26:03.920 --> 26:06.250
Bai Shuo is being protected by Fan Yue.

26:06.770 --> 26:08.200
Even if Eternals and demons are not convinced,

26:08.230 --> 26:09.670
they dare not speak out their anger.

26:10.370 --> 26:11.830
Cold Spring Palace

26:11.860 --> 26:13.240
has seen Yi City's good faith.

26:16.720 --> 26:19.180
You're Lady Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace.

26:19.280 --> 26:20.280
Please forgive me for being disrespectful.

26:20.670 --> 26:21.750
Greetings, Your Majesty.

26:23.010 --> 26:24.890
You offered your blood as a sacrifice to King Yi's Sword

26:24.910 --> 26:26.950
and made the two Heart Flames come into the world in advance.

26:27.000 --> 26:28.360
The Grand Master was very touched.

26:28.380 --> 26:29.640
Since we're cooperating,

26:29.660 --> 26:31.320
we'll both benefit from it.

26:31.340 --> 26:34.370
Surely I won't take it lightly.

26:34.400 --> 26:36.250
Your Majesty, please hurry up

26:36.270 --> 26:37.470
in case

26:37.660 --> 26:38.980
something unfavorable happens.

26:54.910 --> 26:55.590
It's over there, too!

26:55.590 --> 26:56.640
Did you see the dark shape just now?

26:56.660 --> 26:57.260
Hurry!

26:57.750 --> 26:58.580
It's over there! Look!

26:59.210 --> 27:00.620
It's over there!

27:00.680 --> 27:01.540
-Over there.
-Over there.

27:01.610 --> 27:02.480
What's over there?

27:02.510 --> 27:03.290
A dark shape?

27:04.230 --> 27:05.090
What is it?

27:07.110 --> 27:08.350
It actually has an evil aura.

27:08.350 --> 27:09.750
I think it must be an evil cultivator.

27:13.170 --> 27:14.570
It's there, too. Look!

27:16.000 --> 27:17.380
It's the monster from yesterday.

27:18.460 --> 27:19.650
It went that way!

27:21.110 --> 27:22.180
Over there!

27:22.360 --> 27:22.950
Go after it!

27:23.000 --> 27:23.410
Let's go! Hurry!

27:23.440 --> 27:24.350
-Let's go!
-Let's go after it!

27:25.140 --> 27:26.270
Don't you think it's suspicious?

27:26.290 --> 27:28.160
The monster knew Eternals and demons wouldn't let evil cultivators go,

27:28.220 --> 27:29.260
but it still came.

27:29.910 --> 27:30.790
I know.

27:30.810 --> 27:31.980
Yet you still want to chase it?

27:32.010 --> 27:33.130
Only after chasing it

27:33.150 --> 27:34.820
will we know what conspiracy is lying ahead.

27:34.880 --> 27:35.730
Let's go.

27:39.000 --> 27:40.920
Senior, shall we chase it?

27:40.940 --> 27:41.830
You stay in the inn.

27:41.860 --> 27:43.490
If anything happens, you can back us up anytime.

27:43.510 --> 27:44.400
You two, come with me.

27:44.440 --> 27:44.980
Yes.

27:49.210 --> 27:49.900
Go!

27:52.750 --> 27:54.650
-Hurry! It's over there!
-Go after it!

27:54.790 --> 27:55.510
Hurry!

27:57.060 --> 27:58.020
Over there!

27:59.950 --> 28:00.670
Hurry!

28:04.310 --> 28:05.240
Over there!

28:14.330 --> 28:15.260
Catch up with it!

28:34.110 --> 28:35.060
Damn it!

28:35.480 --> 28:37.000
The monster got away.

28:38.160 --> 28:39.120
There's someone over there.

28:51.070 --> 28:51.880
Where are we?

28:52.290 --> 28:53.400
The Yi Clan Tomb.

28:53.680 --> 28:54.570
The Yi Clan Tomb?

28:55.140 --> 28:57.050
How come I don't see any tombstone?

28:57.200 --> 28:58.380
Whose tomb is that?

28:58.820 --> 29:00.010
Yi citizens have a custom

29:00.040 --> 29:02.040
of burying the dead in the open without a tombstone.

29:02.950 --> 29:05.210
However, it's not a Yi citizen buried in the tomb

29:05.240 --> 29:05.960
but...

29:07.810 --> 29:09.110
That's the Wutong Heart Flame.

29:11.630 --> 29:13.110
-It's really the Wutong Heart Flame.
-Really?

29:15.120 --> 29:16.240
Heart Flame?

29:16.730 --> 29:17.510
Over there.

29:18.230 --> 29:20.400
The quietness was so good.

29:22.260 --> 29:24.020
Now, there are so many people

29:24.040 --> 29:25.580
disturbing my peace.

29:27.030 --> 29:28.680
Killing people

29:28.720 --> 29:29.590
is not tiring.

29:33.270 --> 29:34.480
Burying them

29:35.930 --> 29:36.680
is.

29:37.560 --> 29:38.620
What's going on?

29:43.020 --> 29:44.140
Sir,

29:44.210 --> 29:45.030
we are not here

29:45.030 --> 29:46.410
to steal the Heart Flame.

29:46.440 --> 29:48.090
Instead, we chased a monster here.

29:48.110 --> 29:49.750
Since the monster is gone,

29:49.770 --> 29:51.440
we shall take our leave.

29:51.470 --> 29:52.670
Please forgive us

29:52.690 --> 29:54.100
if we offended you.

29:55.010 --> 29:56.170
Why are we leaving?

29:56.190 --> 29:57.520
The Heart Flame is right over there.

29:57.770 --> 29:58.960
It's dangerous here.

29:58.990 --> 30:00.230
We'd better go back

30:00.250 --> 30:01.410
and take some time to think of a solid plan.

30:02.180 --> 30:03.510
This Heart Flame

30:03.540 --> 30:04.570
is mine!

30:05.910 --> 30:07.210
Calm down.

30:21.030 --> 30:21.870
That's impossible.

30:22.490 --> 30:23.630
Isn't there a Magic Restriction in Yi City?

30:23.680 --> 30:25.120
Why can you use magic?

30:25.600 --> 30:26.980
Are you a Yi citizen?

30:29.500 --> 30:30.110
Master,

30:30.140 --> 30:30.820
let's go now.

30:31.090 --> 30:31.930
We can't leave.

30:32.710 --> 30:34.360
Since you're here,

30:34.380 --> 30:35.730
stay here

30:35.760 --> 30:36.790
with me.

30:38.220 --> 30:39.900
I don't care who you are.

30:39.930 --> 30:41.060
I'm taking

30:41.080 --> 30:42.600
this Heart Flame.

30:43.680 --> 30:44.480
Tian Huo.

31:26.430 --> 31:27.950
How did he turn into this?

31:28.280 --> 31:29.740
This is what he originally looks like.

31:35.500 --> 31:37.060
The Snow Lotus Holy Sword.

31:37.420 --> 31:38.380
Could he

31:38.410 --> 31:39.060
be...

31:39.630 --> 31:40.650
Kneel down and bow.

31:41.200 --> 31:42.420
Mr. Rong Xian.

31:42.510 --> 31:43.350
How's that possible?

31:42.670 --> 31:44.040
[Rong Xian, Eternal, Saint of Kunlun]

31:44.080 --> 31:46.450
Didn't Mr. Rong Xian die 1,000 years ago?

31:50.960 --> 31:53.850
How could someone who died 1,000 years ago still be here?

31:56.460 --> 31:57.850
Rong Xian.

31:59.410 --> 32:01.300
He's long dead.

32:03.830 --> 32:05.560
I'll kill all of you, too!

32:22.970 --> 32:24.010
Bastard Rong Xian,

32:24.040 --> 32:25.100
I'll kill you!

32:27.450 --> 32:28.880
Young Master Mu Jiu, why are you here?

32:43.070 --> 32:44.770
[Mu Jiu, demon, Young Master of the Fox Clan]

32:50.030 --> 32:51.170
How could this happen?

32:51.920 --> 32:53.120
He is not Rong Xian.

32:53.730 --> 32:55.870
He's just the resentment formed from Rong Xian's obsession.

32:56.330 --> 32:57.730
Is he himself

32:57.760 --> 32:59.150
buried in the tomb?

32:59.370 --> 33:00.540
He was formed from resentment,

33:01.390 --> 33:03.190
so he's not bound by the rules of Yi City.

33:03.720 --> 33:05.100
We can't kill him,

33:05.120 --> 33:06.490
but he can hurt us.

33:06.520 --> 33:08.150
Doesn't that mean he's invincible?

33:08.880 --> 33:10.830
We'll all die if we stay here any longer.

33:10.860 --> 33:12.060
Let's come back for the Heart Flame

33:12.080 --> 33:13.190
after finding a way

33:13.220 --> 33:14.630
to eliminate the resentment.

33:16.710 --> 33:17.640
The Fox Clan?

33:19.100 --> 33:20.030
Get lost.

33:21.020 --> 33:22.430
Get lost!

33:23.180 --> 33:25.290
I must destroy this bastard's tomb today

33:25.310 --> 33:26.990
to avenge the Fox Clan

33:27.020 --> 33:28.170
and Saintess Ling Long!

33:35.470 --> 33:36.720
Idiot.

33:58.730 --> 33:59.620
Watch out!

34:58.100 --> 34:59.330
Master, go.

34:59.410 --> 35:01.300
Rong Xian's resentment is too strong.

35:01.330 --> 35:03.440
My spirit shield won't last long.

35:05.030 --> 35:05.710
Chong Zhao!

35:06.590 --> 35:07.750
Don't come over here!

35:08.070 --> 35:08.630
Bai Shuo!

36:20.000 --> 36:21.110
Where are we?

36:22.960 --> 36:24.490
Why are you in the Fox Clan's costume?

36:25.180 --> 36:25.900
Yes.

36:25.930 --> 36:27.370
Why are you in the Fox Clan's costume, too?

36:27.390 --> 36:28.870
Well, you, too.

36:30.100 --> 36:31.220
Who changed my clothes?

36:31.920 --> 36:33.170
Why are you looking at me?

36:33.190 --> 36:33.940
Could it be...

36:34.570 --> 36:35.470
me?

36:35.950 --> 36:37.870
Weren't we at the Yi Clan Tomb?

36:37.900 --> 36:39.230
How did we suddenly get here?

36:39.340 --> 36:40.450
Where are we?

36:41.110 --> 36:42.470
[Kunlun]

36:41.170 --> 36:43.000
This is my home, Kunlun.

36:43.750 --> 36:45.010
[Kunlun]

36:45.800 --> 36:46.630
Kunlun?

36:46.630 --> 36:47.230
Kunlun?

36:48.720 --> 36:49.400
No.

36:49.420 --> 36:50.870
Something's wrong here.

36:51.400 --> 36:52.320
What's wrong?

36:53.230 --> 36:54.290
Wuji Palace

36:54.700 --> 36:56.660
was destroyed 1,000 years ago.

36:56.280 --> 36:58.580
[Kunlun]

37:02.140 --> 37:03.030
Wu.

37:08.330 --> 37:09.250
Wu.

37:09.280 --> 37:11.360
I told you not to come, but you didn't listen.

37:11.380 --> 37:12.370
If I hadn't sent the Fox Clan's letter of peace

37:12.400 --> 37:13.900
up the mountain in advance,

37:13.920 --> 37:15.960
you'd have been riddled

37:15.990 --> 37:16.950
before entering the mountain gate

37:16.970 --> 37:18.300
for breaking into Kunlun so rashly.

37:18.330 --> 37:19.640
Who is she?

37:19.670 --> 37:20.840
And who's Wu?

37:21.520 --> 37:22.400
And you.

37:22.430 --> 37:23.280
Qi.

37:23.300 --> 37:25.530
Aren't you the most down-to-earth and stablest servant?

37:25.560 --> 37:27.710
Why did you let the lady sneak out this time?

37:27.730 --> 37:28.960
If anything goes wrong,

37:28.990 --> 37:30.720
no punishment will be enough.

37:31.410 --> 37:32.500
Qi?

37:32.560 --> 37:33.840
Servant?

37:33.870 --> 37:34.760
Me?

37:34.780 --> 37:35.700
Lady?

37:35.730 --> 37:36.670
What lady?

37:36.690 --> 37:37.960
What family am I from?

37:37.990 --> 37:38.990
What about me?

37:39.010 --> 37:40.300
Who am I?

37:40.330 --> 37:42.650
Look how dumb you are.

37:42.670 --> 37:44.350
The Elder must have been out of his mind

37:44.380 --> 37:46.130
to ask the three of you to help me steal the Snow Lotus.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.280
Steal the Snow Lotus?

37:48.510 --> 37:49.760
Especially you,

37:49.780 --> 37:50.660
Ba.

37:50.690 --> 37:52.210
You're usually the most impatient.

37:52.240 --> 37:52.840
If Qi

37:52.860 --> 37:54.490
hadn't been putting in a good word for you with the Elder,

37:54.520 --> 37:55.160
he wouldn't have given you

37:55.180 --> 37:57.180
the chance to make a contribution.

37:57.230 --> 37:58.280
-When we enter Kunlun later,
-The Elder?

37:58.280 --> 37:59.490
control your temper

37:59.510 --> 38:01.320
and don't get into a fight on their turf.

38:01.350 --> 38:02.380
Got it?

38:02.400 --> 38:03.370
I'm Ba.

38:03.400 --> 38:04.540
Ba is me.

38:04.760 --> 38:05.980
Shall I say "got it"?

38:08.400 --> 38:10.560
Aren't you usually good at quarreling?

38:10.580 --> 38:11.910
Why aren't you talking today?

38:11.940 --> 38:12.900
Say something.

38:16.690 --> 38:17.790
Got it.

38:18.220 --> 38:19.010
I won't quarrel with others.

38:21.410 --> 38:23.610
What's going on?

38:23.760 --> 38:25.070
The situation is unclear.

38:25.090 --> 38:26.150
Let's listen more and talk less.

38:26.740 --> 38:27.780
Young Chief Ling Long.

38:29.050 --> 38:30.860
Our Sect Leader has received the Fox Clan's letter.

38:30.890 --> 38:32.030
Please follow us into the mountain.

38:32.480 --> 38:33.730
Ling Long?

38:33.280 --> 38:34.580
[Ling Long, demon, Saintess of the Fox Clan]

38:33.760 --> 38:34.840
Saintess of the Fox Clan!

38:35.050 --> 38:35.930
Thank you.

38:37.930 --> 38:38.900
Snow Lotus.

38:38.930 --> 38:40.080
Saintess Ling Long.

38:40.100 --> 38:41.270
Now I remember!

38:44.170 --> 38:44.960
Let's go.

38:50.300 --> 38:56.470
[Kunlun Sect, Eternal Race]

39:06.730 --> 39:07.760
Everyone!

39:08.410 --> 39:09.530
Hold your breath.

39:09.560 --> 39:10.530
Concentrate.

39:10.920 --> 39:12.420
As disciples of Kunlun,

39:12.780 --> 39:15.080
always remember that the Fox Clan is vicious and cunning.

39:15.320 --> 39:16.790
We, Kunlun,

39:16.810 --> 39:17.970
see them as our mortal enemies.

39:19.010 --> 39:21.710
Who can tell me what happened?

39:22.400 --> 39:24.430
Wasn't I at Yi City just now?

39:24.670 --> 39:26.300
How did I suddenly arrive at Kunlun?

39:28.130 --> 39:30.740
Kunlun is the sworn enemy of the Fox Clan.

39:31.250 --> 39:32.290
If I enter Kunlun,

39:32.320 --> 39:33.880
it'll be like a sheep entering the tiger's den.

39:33.900 --> 39:34.490
Stop!

39:40.650 --> 39:41.420
What are you doing?

39:41.820 --> 39:42.650
W-What are you doing?

39:42.680 --> 39:43.520
Why is he walking over?

39:43.850 --> 39:45.180
Is he going to kill me?

39:45.710 --> 39:46.940
Should I make the first move?

39:47.400 --> 39:48.070
But with so many of them,

39:48.090 --> 39:49.420
I don't stand a chance!

39:49.810 --> 39:50.480
Calm down.

39:50.510 --> 39:51.360
No action unless

39:51.380 --> 39:52.300
the enemy acts first.

39:52.330 --> 39:53.690
Slacking off again? Start practicing now!

39:54.120 --> 39:54.900
Practice?

39:55.580 --> 39:56.620
Practice what?

39:56.650 --> 39:57.580
As disciples of Kunlun,

39:57.600 --> 39:58.770
we are practicing our swordsmanship, of course.

39:59.830 --> 40:01.420
How did I become a disciple of Kunlun?

40:02.000 --> 40:03.080
Kunlun Sword?

40:03.820 --> 40:04.880
How could something so treacherous

40:04.880 --> 40:05.860
end up in my hands?

40:07.650 --> 40:08.480
Take it.

40:10.640 --> 40:11.450
Make your move.

40:11.610 --> 40:13.730
I'm full of demonic aura.

40:13.820 --> 40:14.830
If I make a move,

40:14.860 --> 40:16.610
wouldn't I be exposed immediately?

40:16.670 --> 40:17.460
Could it be that

40:17.490 --> 40:19.480
I'm going to perish here today?

40:19.550 --> 40:20.540
If you are this lazy,

40:20.570 --> 40:22.090
how will you kill fox demons in the future?

40:22.110 --> 40:23.010
Make your move!

40:23.040 --> 40:25.000
Let me test you.

40:25.020 --> 40:25.750
Whatever.

40:25.780 --> 40:26.820
If I die, so be it.

40:29.730 --> 40:31.320
When did I learn the Kunlun Sword Technique?

40:33.670 --> 40:34.470
Wait.

40:35.000 --> 40:36.600
How did I become an Eternal?

40:39.630 --> 40:40.420
Stop!

40:45.200 --> 40:46.330
Rong Xian.

40:46.890 --> 40:48.850
Wasn't Rong Xian at the Yi Clan Tomb just now?

40:49.580 --> 40:50.580
If so, who is this?

40:51.230 --> 40:52.440
What time is it now?

40:52.810 --> 40:53.920
And who am I?

40:54.880 --> 40:55.510
Sir.

40:59.960 --> 41:01.480
Why are you fighting each other?

41:01.510 --> 41:02.160
Sir.

41:02.180 --> 41:02.970
The Elder has ordered

41:03.000 --> 41:04.370
for us disciples to practice our swordsmanship

41:04.390 --> 41:06.260
so that we are ready to fight the Fox Clan any time.

41:06.290 --> 41:07.850
But he slacked off

41:07.870 --> 41:08.500
and refused to practice.

41:08.530 --> 41:09.050
I...

41:09.840 --> 41:10.910
I was just punishing him for a bit.

41:13.350 --> 41:14.850
Why aren't you willing to practice your swordsmanship?

41:15.240 --> 41:16.290
Why should I?

41:16.400 --> 41:18.230
Is the sole purpose of spiritual cultivation and becoming a Kunlun disciple

41:18.520 --> 41:19.850
to kill the Fox Clan?

41:20.920 --> 41:22.080
Do we have nothing better to do?

41:30.110 --> 41:31.780
I mean...

41:31.810 --> 41:33.220
the Fox Clan haven't done

41:33.250 --> 41:34.460
anything evil.

41:34.480 --> 41:35.610
Aren't they just...

41:35.730 --> 41:36.650
vain,

41:36.670 --> 41:37.590
gluttonous,

41:37.620 --> 41:38.820
and like to sunbathe every day?

41:38.840 --> 41:40.240
There's no need to fight

41:40.270 --> 41:41.640
the moment we meet.

41:42.980 --> 41:44.460
Judging from what you said,

41:44.490 --> 41:46.090
you seem to know a lot about the Fox Clan...

41:50.230 --> 41:51.910
and seem to have some different views.

41:52.220 --> 41:53.050
Great.

41:53.070 --> 41:54.490
The Fox Clan sent its people to negotiate peace.

41:54.700 --> 41:56.170
I am going to meet the Saintess of Fox Clan.

41:56.930 --> 41:57.970
Come with me.

41:59.850 --> 42:01.040
Saintess of the Fox Clan?

42:02.680 --> 42:04.280
Could it be that...

42:04.300 --> 42:05.670
Saintess Ling Long is alive in this damned place too?

42:07.140 --> 42:08.140
Aren't you going to keep up?

42:11.400 --> 42:12.090
You...

42:26.540 --> 42:28.540
Cang Shan! Cang Shan!

42:38.620 --> 42:39.700
It's useless.

42:40.020 --> 42:40.960
They have entered

42:40.960 --> 42:42.810
the illusion created out of Rong Xian's resentment.

42:42.840 --> 42:44.810
Even if you break open Rong Xian's tomb,

42:44.830 --> 42:46.660
you can only exist in the present time and space.

42:47.150 --> 42:48.350
You won't be able to enter the illusion.

42:48.900 --> 42:50.020
That monster

42:50.050 --> 42:52.130
deliberately led the Eternals and demons towards the Yi Clan Tomb.

42:52.640 --> 42:55.090
You wanted to make use of Rong Xian's resentment to kill the Eternals and demons.

42:55.120 --> 42:56.120
Rong Xian's illusion

42:56.140 --> 42:57.880
is the second stage of Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

42:57.910 --> 42:58.890
If you desire the Heart Flame,

42:58.920 --> 42:59.850
you must break through the illusion.

42:59.890 --> 43:00.560
This is the rule.

43:00.590 --> 43:02.470
Rong Xian's resentment has been building for a thousand years.

43:02.490 --> 43:03.770
How can it be broken in a moment?

43:03.800 --> 43:04.990
Well then, let's see if

43:05.010 --> 43:06.170
Demon King from the Polar Region

43:06.200 --> 43:07.810
lives up to his name.

43:09.020 --> 43:10.710
I will say just one thing today.

43:10.730 --> 43:12.660
If anything happens to our master,

43:12.680 --> 43:13.670
I will certainly lead

43:13.670 --> 43:16.060
our demons from Bright Moon Palace to crush Yi City.

43:16.090 --> 43:17.340
At the very least,

43:17.720 --> 43:19.160
Yi City has raised you.

43:20.850 --> 43:23.130
You and your king have no grounds to speak of grace.

43:23.160 --> 43:25.530
If my master does not return safely,

43:25.710 --> 43:27.600
your entire city will pay the price.

43:31.830 --> 43:33.470
I think I understand what's going on.

43:33.490 --> 43:34.300
While Ling Ling is not here,

43:34.390 --> 43:35.770
let's figure it out among ourselves.

43:36.370 --> 43:38.000
This time, the Fox Clan came to Kunlun

43:38.020 --> 43:39.100
seemingly for a peace negotiation,

43:39.160 --> 43:41.080
but it's actually to steal the Snow Lotus of Kunlun

43:41.110 --> 43:42.710
to extend the Chief's life.

43:44.910 --> 43:46.790
But didn't Ling Long and Rong Xian

43:46.810 --> 43:48.280
die a long time ago?

43:48.480 --> 43:49.690
Could it be that the Desireless Stone

43:49.720 --> 43:51.360
brought us back to a few thousand years ago?

43:51.380 --> 43:52.970
This is not the true version of a thousand years ago.

43:53.000 --> 43:54.840
This is the realm of illusion from Rong Xian's resentment.

44:02.150 --> 44:03.280
Yi City's Magic Restriction?

44:03.310 --> 44:04.340
This really is the realm of resentment.

44:04.790 --> 44:06.460
What brought us in here was the Desireless Stone.

44:06.480 --> 44:07.780
But what's trapping us now

44:07.810 --> 44:09.160
is Rong Xian's resentment.

44:09.180 --> 44:10.330
Why so?

44:10.360 --> 44:11.770
If it weren't for his will,

44:11.800 --> 44:12.880
we wouldn't have become

44:12.880 --> 44:14.620
people who were already part of his memory.

44:14.650 --> 44:16.360
Then, how will we get out?

44:16.380 --> 44:18.070
If we follow his life until death,

44:18.600 --> 44:19.840
this illusion will naturally be broken.

44:19.860 --> 44:21.370
How could this be?

44:21.400 --> 44:23.210
What if he lives for decades?

44:23.230 --> 44:24.060
Are we going to remain here

44:24.090 --> 44:25.600
and be foxes for decades?

44:28.070 --> 44:29.760
The Saint wouldn't live for that long.

44:30.710 --> 44:31.960
Oh right.

44:31.960 --> 44:33.590
You're a Kunlun disciple.

44:33.960 --> 44:35.170
Tell us then.

44:35.190 --> 44:37.590
What happened a thousand years ago?
